# APP::APP_SET_APP

## Summary
Sets the current app

## Parameters
* **STRING** name

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Called in the gamescripts like:
APP::APP_SET_APP("car");
APP::APP_SET_APP("dog");
